name: Basic Cupcakes Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 200Â°C. Line a 12-hole medium muffin tray with paper cases.
Combine self-raising flour and caster sugar in a large bowl. Whisk butter, eggs, milk and vanilla extract in a bowl. Add butter mixture to flour mixture and gently stir until combined.
Divide batter evenly between paper cases. Bake for 15-20 minutes or until cakes are cooked through when tested with a skewer.
Transfer to a wire rack to cool. When cold, decorate as desired.
